`8Keywords``   : Cure_Blindness
`8Categories`` : 
`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``

`8Syntax:`` 

 * cast 'cure blindness' <character>

 This reverses the effect of blindness, much like Polgara did for old Martje in
Val Alorn.

